tables.table_schema: CREATE TABLE properties (property_id INT PRIMARY KEY, property_name VARCHAR(255), property_type VARCHAR(50));
CREATE TABLE reports (report_id INT PRIMARY KEY, property_id INT, report_date DATE, total_properties INT);

CREATE TABLE properties (
    property_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    property_type VARCHAR(50),
    address TEXT,
    city VARCHAR(50),
    state VARCHAR(50),
    zip_code VARCHAR(10),
    owner_id UUID
);

CREATE TABLE property_mapping (
  mapping_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  property_id INT NOT NULL,
  portfolio_id INT NOT NULL,
  FOREIGN KEY (property_id) REFERENCES property_types(property_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (portfolio_id) REFERENCES portfolio(portfolio_id)
);
